name: Inactive Swayam Sevika List
query:
SELECT 
    employee_id AS `Employee ID`, 
    emp_full_name AS `Employee Name`, 
    designation AS `Designation`, 
    region AS `Region`, 
    district AS `District`,
    branch AS `Branch`, 
    ss_code AS `SS Code`,  
    full_name AS `Swayam Sevika Name`,
    city AS `City`
FROM 
    `tabMy Swayam Sevika`
WHERE
    status = 'Approved' AND
    active = 0
ORDER BY
    CAST(employee_id AS UNSIGNED) ASC;
